{"tid":1881001,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"俄羅斯士兵以十五架T-72B3雪地圍成心形 成功於情人節向女友求婚","createTime":"2020-02-15T08:58:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T16:03:48.000Z","uid":133680,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ff1426cacd6fac4eace0e988db323e08f11d292b","tid":1881001,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T08:58:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php%3fnews_id=1645765\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Famp%2Famp_news.php%253fnews_id%3D1645765&d=uD1rvIJwXfBqs1i1iclFx63e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=34bb10fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php%3fnews_id=1645765</a><br />\n ▲許多人都嚮往浪漫的求婚，俄羅斯一位陸軍中尉用15輛坦克排出愛心求婚。（圖／達志影像／示意圖）<br />\n<br />\n實習記者簡立宇／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯一位陸軍中尉在情人節向女友求婚，找來15輛T-72B3戰車在雪地上排成愛心。兩人站在愛心中央，中尉手抱紅玫瑰單膝下跪向女友問道，「妳我歷經距離和時間考驗，在一起這麼久了，妳願意嫁給我嗎？」，女友最後含羞答應。<br />\n<br />\n根據俄羅斯《紅星電視台》報導，這場浪漫求婚發生在莫斯科附近的阿拉賓諾訓練場，靄靄雪地中排成巨大愛心的坦克車，讓這場求婚變得浪漫壯闊。他們的婚禮可能在今年夏天的坦克兩項軍事比賽期間舉行。"},{"pid":"6400021a486c1c196c4fe1f899e165273eec333b","tid":1881001,"uid":72749,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:00:31.000Z","msg":"坦克車震<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bded256e83886ba85bfd37ba62046792fdadba5","tid":1881001,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:07:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b8c83226b803735bdecf8d9fbee470497eb03d","tid":1881001,"uid":68896,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:10:38.000Z","msg":"公器私用"},{"pid":"6342d11f6e7a4499327ad98195dfe0c18f2b4347","tid":1881001,"uid":183486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:11:13.000Z","msg":"全部一齊開禮炮<img s